data.description: Beautiful, updated 4 Bedroom - 2.5 bath split level. This home is move in ready! Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, extra cabinet space and sliding glass doors that open up to a large outdoor patio plus a very nice landscaped yard! Neutral decor & 6-panel doors throughout, updated tiled bathrooms with granite countertops. Primary bedroom has a full private bathroom. Additional lower level family room with 1/2 bathroom, large laundry room w/ plenty of storage and 4th bedroom. Fully fenced in yard, two car garage. Priced to sell! ***Home will be sold as a SHORT SALE, It has been bank approved for quick, easy close - Home is being sold "AS IS"
